---
---
<section class="py-24 px-8 md:px-24 bg-[#ddffe2]">
    <div class="flex justify-between items-end mb-16">
        <div>
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-headline font-black uppercase tracking-tighter speed-line italic">Noticias Recientes</h2>
            <p class="text-[#3b6447] mt-2">Los hitos que marcan nuestra historia.</p>
        </div>
        <button class="text-[#006b1b] font-headline font-bold uppercase flex items-center gap-2 hover:gap-4 transition-all">Ver Todas <span class="material-symbols-outlined">arrow_forward</span></button>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-6">
        <!-- Main News Feature -->
        <div class="md:col-span-7 group cursor-pointer relative overflow-hidden bg-[#acecbb] h-[500px] rounded-xl">
            <img 
                class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-110" 
                src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1552674605-db6ffd4facb5?q=80&w=2070&auto=format&fit=crop" 
                alt="Athletes celebrating"
                referrerpolicy="no-referrer"
            />
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-[#001205] via-transparent to-transparent"></div>
            <div class="absolute bottom-0 p-10">
                <span class="bg-[#4252b4] text-[#f3f1ff] px-3 py-1 text-xs font-headline font-bold uppercase mb-4 inline-block">Nacionales 2024</span>
                <h3 class="text-4xl font-headline font-black text-white uppercase tracking-tighter italic group-hover:text-[#fdd835] transition-colors">Histórico ORO en Relevos 4x100</h3>
                <p class="text-[#acecbb] mt-4 line-clamp-2 max-w-lg">El equipo chocoano pulverizó el cronómetro en el Estadio de Quibdó, estableciendo una nueva marca regional y asegurando el pase a los Panamericanos.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="md:col-span-5 grid grid-rows-2 gap-6">
            <!-- News Card 2 -->
            <div class="bg-[#cafdd4] p-8 group hover:bg-[#ddffe2] transition-all rounded-xl">
                <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-4">
                    <span class="text-[#4252b4] font-bold text-xs uppercase">Anuncio Oficial</span>
                    <span class="text-[#3b6447] text-sm">Hace 2 horas</span>
                </div>
                <h4 class="text-2xl font-headline font-black uppercase tracking-tight group-hover:text-[#006b1b] transition-colors">Nueva Pista de Atletismo en Istmina</h4>
                <p class="text-[#3b6447] mt-3">Infraestructura de clase mundial llega para potenciar el semillero del Chocó.</p>
                <div class="mt-6 flex gap-4">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[#006b1b]">location_on</span>
                    <span class="font-bold">Istmina, Chocó</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- News Card 3 -->
            <div class="bg-[#006b1b] text-[#d1ffc8] p-8 group relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl">
                <div class="absolute -right-10 -bottom-10 opacity-10">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[200px]">sports_score</span>
                </div>
                <h4 class="text-2xl font-headline font-black uppercase tracking-tight italic">Resultados Intercolegiales</h4>
                <p class="mt-3 opacity-90">Descarga el PDF completo con las marcas y clasificaciones de la jornada juvenil.</p>
                <button class="mt-8 bg-[#d1ffc8] text-[#006b1b] px-6 py-2 font-headline font-bold uppercase text-sm transition-transform hover:scale-105 active:scale-95">Descargar PDF</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
